# JavaScript Function Basics

```javascript
// Function to add two numbers
function add(a, b) {
    return a + b;
}

// Function usage
const sum = add(3, 4);
console.log('Sum:', sum);
```

### Function Flow:

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Input Numbers]
    A --> B[Call add Function]
    B --> C[Perform Addition]
    C --> D[Return Result]
    D --> E[Output Sum]
```
